cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about fine-grained image classification using deep convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach for combining multiple DCNNs, which involves joint end-to-end training, so it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, since the paper deals with image classification, it could also be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
